title: [1962] Art Blakey - Three Blind Mice Vol. 1 (320kbps)
description:
Art Blakey & The Jazz Messengers live album from 1962. Recorded live at the Renaissance Club, Hollywood in March of 1962. Includes musicians such as Freddie Hubbard on trumpet, Curtis Fuller on trombone, Wayne Shorter on tenor sax, Cedar Walton on piano, & Jymie Merritt on bass. 



01. Three Blind Mice                    [8:17 ]
02. Blue Moon                           [5:59 ]
03. That Old Feeling                    [6:34 ]
04. Plexis                              [5:49 ]
05. Up Jumped Spring                    [9:45 ]
06. Up Jumped Spring (Alternate Take)   [5:16 ]
07. When Lights Are Low                 [4:08 ]
08. Children of The Night               [8:12 ]


Tracks 6 & 8 were not on the original LP.
